      "text": "8. Installation Precautions"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Installation is the reverse of the removal procedure."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "O-rings shall be replaced upon disassembly.",
        "When replenishing cooling water, do not allow the cooling water to adhere to electrical components or painted surfaces. If it does adhere, wipe it off immediately."
